{"tid":2167649,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黎生之哭 - 蔣芸","createTime":"2020-08-21T08:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T09:02:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1feb2aabf3f28c494968055f3e15982eb0475e05","tid":2167649,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/NNHMF33RHJB6RLYXGNFNXFAE3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FNNHMF33RHJB6RLYXGNFNXFAE3Q%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu0zob1WjLKDnR9IVaUJYWuI%3D&h=ea5e16b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FNNHMF33RHJB6RLYXGNFNXFAE3Q%2F&h=8e2bf7d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/NNHMF33RHJB6RLYXGNFNXFAE3Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n黎生之哭 - 蔣芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fZ3j-tbxFUtIOBl_GY4fAyFnH3M=/763x482/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TSYOR5XF3RESDESOUFZW23EWEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfZ3j-tbxFUtIOBl_GY4fAyFnH3M%3D%2F763x482%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTSYOR5XF3RESDESOUFZW23EWEU.jpg&h=f16fe374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看肥佬黎和林夕對談直播乃廢然而嘆！唉兩個君子人、兩個老實人，而且太君子太老實了，怎麼應付眼下這詭譎多變奸險狡詐的現實困境啊。<br />\n<br />\n肥佬黎在直播中流下了男人的眼淚感觸尤大，想起歷史上楚漢相爭的年代；楚霸王俘虜了劉邦父親，威脅他若不投降，就將劉父烹而食之，高台案板已設好，柴火亦已燒旺，被俘虜的劉父綁在案上，此時，只聽到劉邦閒閒地說咱們當年曾結拜為兄弟，我父即是你父，你如果一定要把他煮來吃，請分我一杯羹&hellip;&hellip;。以上就記憶所及零碎道來，你看劉邦有多奸，項羽何曾是他的對手，至少先解了老父之危；後來成敗已載於史，大家都知道了。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，他愴然淚下，泣不成聲，林夕弱弱的安慰道：沒發生的事，多想也無益。 。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。；正如被釋後的肥佬黎回報館也曾說出好彩！沒有被送中&hellip;&hellip;。<br />\n<br />\n人們所耽心的、所耿耿於。。。。。。。。。。不承認都已如是不講法理。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。他是哭今日之香港，哭今日香港不知究竟還剩下了什麼？"},{"pid":"7a1a1485627517e8605e7d6f1e106b4cc4909361","tid":2167649,"uid":214594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:49:40.000Z","msg":"南風喃，北海北 <br />\n北海有墓碑"},{"pid":"9bfe993b8a6915bba6c83dffecef33de14aa76d4","tid":2167649,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:02:37.000Z","msg":"睇咗蔣麗芸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}